title: Date of the contract
explanation: Date explicitly stated as 'dated as of November 4,2016' in the contract header.

title: Party A
explanation: Party A identified as 'MUFG Union Bank, N.A.' in the introductory paragraph.

title: party_B
explanation: Party B identified as 'Pricesmart, Inc.' in the introductory paragraph.

title: Specified entity Party A
explanation: Text states 'Specified Entity' means in relation to Party A: None.

title: Specified entity Party B
explanation: Text states 'Specified Entity' means in relation to Party B: Any Affiliate.

title: Specified transaction scope
explanation: The text states that 'Specified Transaction' has the meaning specified in Section 14, indicating the standard scope as per Section 14.

title: Cross default applicable parties
explanation: The text states that the 'Cross Default' provisions apply to Party A and Party B.

title: Specified indebtness includes borrowed_money
explanation: The text does not explicitly mention borrowed money as included or excluded in Specified Indebtedness.

title: Specified indebtness excludes deposits
explanation: The text states that for Party A, Specified Indebtedness shall not include deposits received in the normal course of business, indicating deposits are excluded.

title: amount for Party A
explanation: Threshold amount for Party A is specified as a percentage (3%) of Shareholders' Equity, no fixed amount given.

title: currency for Party A
explanation: No currency specified for Party A threshold amount, as it is expressed as a percentage.

title: percentage for Party A
explanation: Threshold amount for Party A is 3% as explicitly stated.

title: percentage reference for Party A
explanation: Percentage reference for Party A is Shareholders' Equity as explicitly stated.

title: amount for Party B
explanation: Threshold amount for Party B is defined by reference to the 'threshold amount' under the Credit Agreement, no fixed amount given.

title: currency for Party B
explanation: No currency specified for Party B threshold amount, as it is defined by reference to another agreement.

title: percentage for Party B
explanation: No percentage specified for Party B threshold amount; it is defined by reference to another agreement.

title: percentage reference for Party B
explanation: No percentage reference specified for Party B threshold amount; it is defined by reference to another agreement.

title: Credit Event Upon Merger  applicable parties
explanation: The text states that 'Credit Event Upon Merger' applies to Party A and Party B.

title: Automatic Early Termination  applicable parties
explanation: The text states that the Automatic Early Termination provision will not apply to Party A and will not apply to Party B, indicating it applies to no party.

title: Termination Currency
explanation: The text defines 'Termination Currency' as United States Dollars, which corresponds to the ISO code USD.

title: Email for notices for Party A
explanation: Email for Party A is explicitly stated twice as ISDAgroup@us.mufg.jp in the addresses for notices.

title: Email for notices for Party B
explanation: Email for Party B is explicitly stated as apatel@pricesmart.com in the address for notices.

title: Process agent for party A
explanation: Text states 'Party A appoints as its Process Agent: Not Applicable.' indicating no process agent for Party A.

title: Name of process agent for party A
explanation: No process agent appointed for Party A as per text.

title: Address of process agent for party A
explanation: No process agent appointed for Party A as per text.

title: Process agent for party B
explanation: Text states 'Party B appoints as its Process Agent: Not Applicable.' indicating no process agent for Party B.

title: Name of process agent for party B
explanation: No process agent appointed for Party B as per text.

title: Address of process agent for party B
explanation: No process agent appointed for Party B as per text.

title: Party A is a Multibranch party
explanation: Text explicitly states 'Party A is not a Multibranch Party'.

title: Party A offices
explanation: Party A may act only through the Los Angeles office as stated.

title: Party B is a Multibranch party
explanation: Text explicitly states 'Party B is not a Multibranch Party'.

title: Party B offices
explanation: No offices listed for Party B since it is not a Multibranch Party.

title: Party for calculation agent
explanation: The text states 'The Calculation Agent is Party A, unless otherwise specified in a Confirmation,' indicating Party A is the default calculation agent.

title: Governing Law
explanation: The text states the agreement is governed by the laws of the State of New York.
